<Defs>

  <ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase">
    <defName>BOB_Yutyrannus</defName>
    <label>yutyrannus</label>
    <devNote>yutyrannus</devNote>
    <description>A shaggy tyrant molded by cold and conflict. Its courage roar surges through allies, hardening their resolve and sharpening their strikes.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Gameplay effect:&lt;/color&gt; When tamed, it can learn a courage roar ability, which increases the melee strength and defenses of friendly pawns that hear it.</description>
